data.description: Embrace the new year with a lucrative investment opportunity! This income-generating duplex awaits a new owner seeking prime real estate in a convenient location near Bay Shore Park, Sylvan Beach Park, and Morgan's Point within The Bay Area. Spanning 1625 square feet, this duplex comprises two units, each offering 2 bedrooms, 1 bath, and generously proportioned living and kitchen spaces. The property features a vast yard space, presenting ample potential for expansion – envisioning the addition of more units, a pool, a playset, and more, allowing for further income growth and development opportunities. Currently, one unit is occupied, while both units will be vacant and primed to generate income post-sale, offering flexibility for the new owner. Whether you're seeking to expand your investment portfolio or delve into real estate, this duplex stands as a promising income-producing property in a desirable area, ready to cater to your investment aspirations.
